<L>__{exterior central american jungle later afternoon}
<A>__{jane in the f.g. with her crew while aaron talks in rapid spanish to the guerrilla leaders.}
<C>__{aaron }
<D>__{are you guys kidding or do you really think you'll run into something...? i mean, do you feel that every time and it never happens? or is it the first time it felt that way and it's going to happen?... i mean, how bad can it be?... are you nervous...? what's the chances on a scale of one to ten that we're going to be in a war within the next few hours?... really?}
<A>__{he starts to walk towards jane one of the men he was talking with calling after him with an added thought.}
